            "aonid": 221,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Monster Core pg. 316",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 316,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "This nonvenomous family of snakes is rarely a threat to anything but small mammals and birds, hunting by coiling around prey and crushing victims with their powerful muscles. Nonetheless, larger pythons can be dangerous due to their strength. Herpetologists sometimes keep pythons as pets.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
